| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5816 — Recovery Inhibition (handala)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: d88198d5-0bc6-57d1-8caf-0e98f2b1ef0c"
